values.text:
Welcome to CryptoJewelry
Collectible NFTs. 

Ground - Animated Designs,
Memory of Smell sculpture
1st Floor - Still Designs
2nd Floor -  Gallery Portal
3rd Floor - Open
Top Floor - Lounge, 
Artchitect's personal gallery

Regardless of the reason behind 
the vision, custom Crypto Jewelry
collectibles are ready to shake 
the world of Crypto. Welcome 
to the future of NFTs collectibles.

The same 3D models can be 
also used as in-game, virtual 
reality assets. Clients will be 
provided with updates
to their orders.

Crypto Jewelry by CinnamonDream 
are the first type of 
CryptoJewelry Collectible NFTs. 
Designs are custom and used 
only once. By owning 
CryptoJewels, you gain access to
their 3D model design, which can 
be used to produce the jewelry 
for yourself, or your loved ones.

Custom jewelry is often a priority
when shopping for artisan jewelry.
Models can be designed 
upon request.
